Description:
Magnificent Modern Renovation with a Family Focus
Instruction is that the property is to be sold by way of online Auction- Friday 2nd October at 5pm- unless negotiated and sold prior.
Beautifully renovated, this modern family home will impress from beginning to end.
Set on a spacious suburban block, the property begins with an open front yard and sun-drenched porch, before you enter onto warming hardwood floors which flow throughout the home.
The semi-formal lounge is flooded with natural light and with a ceiling fan, split system heating/cooling for comfort, before making your way into an open dining room and kitchen precinct.
The kitchen offers stone benches, stainless steel appliances including a built-in gas cooktop, under bench oven (900mm) and range hood. It also has an integrated Asko dishwasher and an island bench to finish off the kitchen experience.
Bedroom accommodation is housed off the hallway where all bedrooms have robes and ceiling fans for comfort, as well as proximity to the bathroom with floor-to-ceiling tiles, corner shower, vanity, separate inset bath and heat light.
A separate laundry provides direct access to a sensational outdoor area, highlighted by a brilliant covered entertaining deck which overlooks plenty of private backyard for the kids and pets to explore.
A double garage/workshop, secure off-street parking options, vegetable patches and gas ducted heating further contributes to an incredible opportunity in a picture perfect location.
Positioned close to all the area has to offer including shopping, schools, cafes and restaurants, with easy access to public transport, major roads, Citylink and Melbourne's Tullamarine Airport, this is a lifestyle choice for the better.

Description:
Room For A Large Family!
This double storey elevated executive residence has been built to a high standard and set amongst quality homes with city views to be enjoyed from the extensive balcony. Beautifully maintained throughout by the same family since new, you are immediately greeted by the light filled entrance that guides you through to the step down formal lounge & formal dining/5th bedroom, leading to the open kitchen & meals area with gas cooking appliances and dish washer. Step outside a separate rumpus or home office with its own entrance and spotless powder room downstairs.
Upstairs comprising 4 carpeted bedrooms with BIRs, plus study served by a large centrally located bathroom. Master bedroom with full ensuite, along with a light filled retreat makes it perfect for families.
Extras include ducted heating, high ceilings, alfresco, Terracotta roof, smoke house, BBQ area, veggie patch and large double brick garage. All this set on a good sized allotment and superbly located in one of the most central and convenient localities, only a short walk to Sunshine Hospital, Ginifer Train Station, host of schools, Holy Eucharist Parish Church, parks and easy access into the CBD via Western Ring Road. With nothing to do except move in, unpack and enjoy, this impressive multi-level home is a dream come true. Call to inspect today!

Description:
Peace, Position And Privacy
With the health and well-being of our community being front of mind we have additional measures in place at all property inspections. Our COVID-19 conditions of entry are available for your viewing click here: https://bit.ly/347XJd6
Space, serenity and low maintenance qualities are pleasing features offered by this single storey three bedroom brick home situated a short distance from Watergardens Shopping Centre, schools and trains. Set behind an attractive façade, this light filled haven enjoys an entry foyer, delightful living area and spacious family/dining zone highlighted by soaring cathedral ceilings with exposed timber beams. Sliding doors reveal a paved alfresco entertaining area and private courtyard garden. The kitchen is well-equipped with gas hob, wall oven, breakfast bar and plentiful timber-fronted cabinetry. Nestled towards the rear are three double bedrooms, all present generous built-in-robes. A family-size bathroom, with built-in bath, timber vanity and corner shower, separate toilet and laundry with extra storage completes the layout. Further highlights include split-system air conditioner, ducted heating, driveway parking and drive through garage with front and rear roller doors. An ideal first home, downsizer or investment with primary and secondary schools, parks, shopping centres, buses and freeways all within easy reach.

Description:
Stylish townhouse - resort-style living
***Please contact us via email or phone to speak about your options to privately inspect this property. Thank you.***
Charming, light-filled townhouse in resort-style estate with valley views and handy to Keilor Road shops, restaurants, schools and public transport. Ideal for first-home buyers, this spacious and modern property boasts two excellent bedrooms - main with large WIR and 2-way ensuite (shower, full bath), alcove/study area, good-sized laundry (storage space) and private courtyard. The bright, family/living area (split system) is open plan with the kitchen (dishwasher, electric oven, gas top) and edged by the large deck overlooking the valley. Plus ducted heating, quality flooring, electronic security gates, remote single-car garage and complex facilities including swimming pool and communal BBQ area. Inspection will impress.
*** COVID-19 ANNOUNCEMENT ***
If you're attending a Private Appointment, we request that you only attend if you are fit and healthy to do so and not under any self-isolation conditions. We request that you maintain a healthy distance from our team members, and if requested wait outside until the property is ready for the appointment. Lastly, please refrain from touching items/fixtures and doors within the properties. If you would like to view something in particular, please request the agent's assistance. Thank you.

Description:
listedAS - Renovated to Perfection
Upon entry is the lounge room that flows through to the beautifully renovated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, ample storage space, and a massive bench top. While you cook, you can look out into the undercover alfresco area and watch your kids run and play in the big north facing backyard.
This friendly floorplan consist of three bedrooms with built-in robes, stunningly, renovated bathroom with separate toilet and big laundry. Additional features include spotted gum flooring throughout, ducted heating, air-conditioning, alarm, 8 cameras, roller shutters, shed, carport, and a double gate which allows you to park multiple cars into your backyard.
Situated on a massive 641m2, there is plenty of room for the whole family. If the kids need a bigger space to run and play then they can walk 7 doors down to the beautiful Biggs Street Reserve where they can play basketball, kick the footy and play in the playground while the parents can exercise on the gym equipment.
Close to St Albans East Primary, St Pauls Catholic School, St Albans Secondary College, Alfrieda Street Shops and Restaurants, and also Keilor Downs Shopping Centre and St Albans Leisure Centre.

Description:
Perfectly Positioned!
To arrange your 15 minute private inspection, contact Luke on 0435 914 910.
This sole owner, architecturally designed and wonderfully built home is sure to impress. Being offered to the market for the first time, this is an extremely rare opportunity to secure a quality home in the heart of Taylors Lakes. This well thought out home has a unique and spacious floor plan comprising three generous size bedrooms, multiple living areas, double car garage and a long driveway that provides extra vehicle parking. High ceilings feature throughout, with a cathedral front room, a spacious north facing kitchen, dining and lounge room beaming with natural light and overlooking the rear garden and linear park area, a real delight.
On an allotment of 750m2 (approx.), this property is positioned in one of the best streets you'll find in Taylors Lakes. Backing onto the walking trail and creek which leads you straight to the Watergardens Shopping Centre less than 250m away, along with other parklands and reserves in very close proximity. Whether it's shopping, exercise, or quick access to essential amenities and services, everything is at your fingertips here.
**COVID 19 Announcement**
At Ray White Taylors Lakes, the health & wellbeing of our clients is our highest priority. Open for inspections have been suspended until further notice as part of our industry initiative & government regulations.
Private inspections, video walk throughs & virtual tours can be arranged.

Description:
Huge Potential
*INSPECTIONS AVAILABLE BY APPOINTMENT*
Set on a good size 580sq. metre allotment in an enviable and tightly held location this sun drenched bright and airy family home will brighter your horizon. With new floating flooring throughout, the home offers three good size bedrooms, all with built in robes, lounge and dining area and a private side facing kitchen and meals area. Includes a gas wall oven, air conditioner, a comfortable under cover entertainment area, a massive rear yard begging for further development and an expansive concrete drive with a steel gate and side fence. A must see property.
COVID-19 UPDATE
We are still conducting business during this time but with the safety & health of others and the team as the highest priority.
We will be conducting private inspections only with stricter guidelines so please contact our office to arrange a viewing.
During our Private Inspections we will ask that only one person is allowed into the property at any time. We ask that no surfaces are touched. We will have the property ready for you to inspect prior to your arrival.
We ask anyone that has recently returned from overseas and if you are unwell to ensure you do not attend any inspections. Contact our office to organise alternative viewing arrangements. This also means if you have been next to anyone that may have been overseas or unwell.
We thank everyone for their co-operation & patience during this time. Stay Safe & Healthy!

Description:
An Easy-Living Oasis of Quality and Privacy
Please register your interest in this property so that we can ensure you are included in the Virtual Auction and/or contacted in the event the property is going to be sold prior to the Virtual Auction 1st October at 3pm.
Due to Melbourne's Stage 4 Restrictions, all Nelson Alexander team members are working from home. Please contact us via email or phone to speak about your options to view this property virtually. Thank you
With its surprisingly spacious floorplan, long list of features and reassuringly secure surrounds, this single-level home delivers an exceptional low-maintenance lifestyle in a prime location walking distance to the best of Niddrie. Flawless presentation throughout, the home's impressive interior showcases a large master bedroom with WIR and private ensuite, two additional bedrooms (both with BIRs) along with a central bathroom (with spa) and separate WC. Adding to its easy-living credentials is a wonderfully spacious open-plan living/dining area accompanied by a stone-bench kitchen with breakfast bar, tiled splashbacks, dishwasher and 900mm cooking appliances. Other highlights of the home include a full-size laundry, split-system heating and cooling, alarm, video intercom and motorized security shutters, as well as solid hardwood floors and high ceilings throughout. Dual outdoor spaces complete the picture including a secluded central courtyard and delightful north-facing backyard with undercover patio, established gardens and high fences for added privacy, plus the advantage of an internally-accessed garage (remote-control) and additional front carport. Perfectly positioned in one of Niddrie's best streets, it's close to Keilor Road trams, popular cafes, renowned restaurants and vibrant shopping centre, as well as primary and secondary schools and easy access to the Calder Freeway.
